-- Castel in Rose Wine Alliance With Vranken-Pommery, Decanter Says
-- B y   G u y   C o l l i n s
-- 2013-11-19T22:56:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-19/castel-in-rose-wine-alliance-with-vranken-pommery-decanter-says.html
French wine companies Castel and
Vranken-Pommery Monopole SA have agreed to form a joint
venture, Listel SA, to focus on selling rose wines globally,
Decanter.com said.  The business will aim to sell 40 million bottles annually,
with Vranken-Pommery retaining ownership of wine estates
including Listel and Billette, while Castel will offer access
to its global distribution, according to Decanter magazineâ€™s
website. There will be particular focus on newer wine markets
such as China, Russia and  Africa , Decanter.com said.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
